item.description:
If you are using Docker for Windows there might be a need to switch between Linux OR Windows container at times.
The first way to achieve this is to right click on the whale icon from the system tray and choose either the option &ldquo;Switch to Linux Containers&hellip;&rdquo; OR &ldquo;Switch to Windows Containers&hellip;&rdquo;
The other way to achieve this from the CMD/Powershell is to execute the below command:  &amp; 'C:\Program Files\Docker\Docker\DockerCli.
